---
title: Greek-Inspired Feta Turkey Meatballs with Roasted Potatoes and Tzatziki
description: Feta cheese is the secret ingredient for giving juicy DIY meatballs a briny, salty pop! Complete this Greek-inspired feast with garlic potatoes and a fresh side salad that will please the whole family.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/boulettes-de-dinde-au-feta-a-la-grecque-c09e42b5.jpg
